entries.femaleVariant: But they promised us a permit. They can't just back out now!
'Course they can. Night Corp coughed up more eddies.
Not how you fucking do things! We had a contract! You break a contract, that's war!
Sure. If the two parties are batting in the same league.
But why? City won't get a damn thing from that development. Night Corp investments fill Night Corp coffers.
Dunno. Maybe they're just stupid. Not everything's some grand conspiracy.
